column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "C7928EE143EAF15CD9259FA8E5D872FC", "Hello, {Player}. Surprise! I opened a clinic!")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "6CFD6AC7409EFC1293CD35A9C42F55C2", "It\'s for treating sickness and injuries. It\'s not free, but it will be cheap.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "5B90F674418410AB7A6359B7D9580DBA", "Your Digimon looks fine. What do you need?")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "CF7D0A554CAAA1F2D4BD6BBA2C12B4F1", "He should be fine.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "676120A842C844044C1DD0B56E36592A", "You don\'t have enough bits. I can\'t sell you that.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "F9A595DB462BCF666FD3D0850B2197B1", "You have too many Items.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "676120A842C844044C1DD0B56E36592A", "You don\'t have enough bits. I can\'t sell you that.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "D04B9723452A5053F333A8B39CF5AEA2", "You have too many Items.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "9767BB5048C6F55BDAFC21AEFFAFD634", "Your Digimon doesn\'t look well. You need to take care of his health.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "522288F6414527E81A2971B0877A994F", "I\'ll treat him now and give you a discount. 300 bits.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "17C387E743E6E57458455A84541EF1B7", "You don\'t have enough bits? Pay me what you can.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "BCA093CD41CDD76DD296FC9D2D9B5B4C", "Everything is ok now. Just be careful from now on.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "85DEB61840F0B86649278F88D9AD702F", "Still need something?")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "9FC16CF34EB87E468995B5B6B2BB069A", "{Partner}\'s Tiredness is very high, he needs to rest now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "2B8663CC46224E1786CE8087D0710489", "{Partner} is tired. He should rest now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "6C982E9D4D6782E4A3FCD3B0B8F18A33", "{Partner} seems to be a bit tired. He shouldn\'t push himself.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "C0E471ED457F5D0C623797AA25CF4D64", "{Partner} is fine. Watch his Tiredness level.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "02A4B2684D9EC8CCD31F3785436112EA", "When he doesn\'t feel good, come see me.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "7348EC6346C8EECFAF62469918985E14", "If he\'s still tired, train less, and make him eat and sleep regularly.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "74F03B0A4DED45C8CC6EB79A75DFAA1F", "Staying in cold or hot places for too long can cause illness.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "E406F5E8420F609A42E07DAC638AA19E", "A bandage is only good for wounds.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "570D67C049710A47BB0C0A83EF5147C6", "You can treat sickness with Medicine, but it won\'t reduce Tiredness.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "3848D494435D08DA248043B7F1FA189F", "If HP is low at the end of a battle, Digimon can get hurt easily.")
NSLOCTEXT("[89D958D342A7540F93828192991B3DE7]", "8B0E05D3478ED56FFD40E0A802558FFA", "Keeping Happiness and Tiredness at good levels leads to long life.")
